headline: American, Southwest Lead Rally Of Airline Stocks
summary: On Tuesday, U.S. airlines stocks rallied after several analysts offered rosy predictions for the industry in 2026.

headline: United Adds New Features to Award-Winning Mobile App Like Virtual Gate, Club Recommendation Tool and Real-Time Bag Tracker
summary: United today launched new features to its award-winning mobile app to save customers even more time and further improve the overall travel experience on the world's largest airline*:
